  "body": "**Bug Template**\r\n\r\n*Description*:\r\n\r\nGiven the `dynamic_resource.lds_config.path` is an invalid path envoy will segfault.\r\n\r\n*Repro steps*:\r\n\r\nThe following shows the steps necessary to repro the issue on the latest envoy\r\n\r\n```\r\nroot@cbc1703eeb58:/# envoy -c /envoy-config/config.yaml --v2-config-only --service-node some-node --service-cluster some-cluster\r\n[2017-12-20 15:02:00.958][17][info][main] source/server/server.cc:185] initializing epoch 0 (hot restart version=9.200.16384.127)\r\n[2017-12-20 15:02:00.983][17][info][upstream] source/common/upstream/cluster_manager_impl.cc:131] cm init: all clusters initialized\r\n[2017-12-20 15:02:00.983][17][info][config] source/server/configuration_impl.cc:46] loading 0 listener(s)\r\n[2017-12-20 15:02:00.983][17][info][config] source/server/configuration_impl.cc:84] loading tracing configuration\r\n[2017-12-20 15:02:00.983][17][info][config] source/server/configuration_impl.cc:110] loading stats sink configuration\r\n[2017-12-20 15:02:00.984][17][info][main] source/server/server.cc:347] all clusters initialized. initializing init manager\r\n[2017-12-20 15:02:00.984][17][critical][backtrace] bazel-out/k8-opt/bin/source/server/_virtual_includes/backtrace_lib/server/backtrace.h:101] Caught Segmentation fault, suspect faulting address 0x0\r\n[2017-12-20 15:02:00.984][17][critical][backtrace] bazel-out/k8-opt/bin/source/server/_virtual_includes/backtrace_lib/server/backtrace.h:85] Backtrace obj<envoy> thr<0> (use tools/stack_decode.py):\r\n[2017-12-20 15:02:00.984][17][critical][backtrace] bazel-out/k8-opt/bin/source/server/_virtual_includes/backtrace_lib/server/backtrace.h:95] thr<0> #0 0x8c88c4\r\n[2017-12-20 15:02:00.984][17][critical][backtrace] bazel-out/k8-opt/bin/source/server/_virtual_includes/backtrace_lib/server/backtrace.h:93] thr<0> obj</lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libpthread.so.0>\r\n[2017-12-20 15:02:00.984][17][critical][backtrace] bazel-out/k8-opt/bin/source/server/_virtual_includes/backtrace_lib/server/backtrace.h:95] thr<0> #1 0x7fe8b741b32f\r\n[2017-12-20 15:02:00.984][17][critical][backtrace] bazel-out/k8-opt/bin/source/server/_virtual_includes/backtrace_lib/server/backtrace.h:97] end backtrace thread 0\r\nSegmentation fault (core dumped)\r\nroot@cbc1703eeb58:/# cat /envoy-config/config.yaml\r\nadmin:\r\n  access_log_path: /dev/null\r\n  address:\r\n    socket_address:\r\n      address: 127.0.0.1\r\n      port_value: 9901\r\n\r\nstatic_resources:\r\n  clusters:\r\n    - name: 0-service-cluster\r\n      connect_timeout: 0.25s\r\n      type: STATIC\r\n      lb_policy: ROUND_ROBIN\r\n      hosts:\r\n        - socket_address:\r\n            address: 127.0.0.1\r\n            port_value: 8080\r\n\r\ndynamic_resources:\r\n  lds_config:\r\n    path: /some/invalid/path.yaml\r\n\r\nroot@cbc1703eeb58:/# envoy --version\r\n\r\nenvoy  version: 3a69c0a47ae5eed6980af6d43e0999e63efe24b2/Clean/RELEASE\r\n```\r\n\r\n*Config*:\r\n\r\nSee the snippet above\r\n\r\n*Logs*:\r\n\r\nSee the snippet above",
